{"type":"message","id":"c18bc232","parentId":"723ab7ee","timestamp":"2026-04-16T08:10:38.345Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Yeah, probably. I can see this new session, but not the old one from here yet, which usually means the previous chat still exists separately rather than being deleted.\n\nIf you want, I can help you recover it fast: either tell me where you were chatting from and what you remember from the last message, or in the UI look for a session/history list and reopen the previous thread. If you want, I can also walk you step by step and help identify which session is the right one.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0156872873475ee30169e0997b2eb481919c8b61ef46e547a3\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":679,"output":110,"cacheRead":12160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12949,"cost":{"input":0.0016975000000000002,"output":0.00165,"cacheRead":0.0030399999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0063875}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776327033400,"responseId":"resp_0156872873475ee30169e099795f988191ac94503ed383cccf"}}
