{"type":"message","id":"e54bde24","parentId":"6fda3d3e","timestamp":"2026-04-16T08:17:45.327Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Glad you got the conversation back.\n\nI don’t see a separate knowledge tab from here. If file attach is being weird, easiest workaround is either paste the compose file directly in chunks, or tell me the path if it already exists in the workspace and I can read it there. If you’d rather just move on, tell me the next step for Aurelius/Apollo and I’ll jump in.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0156872873475ee30169e09b26f1c88191986e07dc618d869c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":208,"output":89,"cacheRead":13056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13353,"cost":{"input":0.0005200000000000001,"output":0.001335,"cacheRead":0.003264,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005119}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776327459602,"responseId":"resp_0156872873475ee30169e09b239d448191a7719a919450c0d3"}}
