{"type":"message","id":"8dcb142d","parentId":"d827533c","timestamp":"2026-04-16T08:21:59.096Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Perfect, that’s enough to re-anchor us.\n\nWe’d gotten to this point:\n- corpus inventory and dedupe were done\n- Apollo/Aurelius classification was refined\n- timelines and project scaffolds were created\n- the next best step was to use the current `docker-compose.yaml` to align the ingestion workflow with the actual running stack\n\nSo unless you want to change course, the next move is: send me the compose file content, or point me to its path in the workspace, and I’ll pick up from there.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0156872873475ee30169e09c24c71c81918af7e44f9d80f14f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":139,"output":117,"cacheRead":18176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18432,"cost":{"input":0.00034750000000000004,"output":0.001755,"cacheRead":0.004543999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0066465}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776327712158,"responseId":"resp_0156872873475ee30169e09c202e288191b2690587fb8a4b76"}}
{"type":"message","id":"20c420ef","parentId":"8dcb142d","timestamp":"2026-04-16T08:23:28.503Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-16 08:23 UTC] for some reason i am not able to attach it but i will paste it here:\nservices:\n # 1. THE INFERENCE ENGINE (5070 Ti Blackwell-Optimized)\n ollama:\n image: ollama/ollama:latest\n container_name: ollama\n restart: unless-stopped\n ports:\n - \"11434:11434\"\n volumes:\n - ./data/ollama:/root/.ollama\n - C:/Apollo/Intel:/root/apollo_intel\n - C:/Apollo/Vault:/root/apollo_vault\n environment:\n - OLLAMA_FLASH_ATTENTION=1\n - OLLAMA_KV_CACHE_TYPE=q4_0 # Optimizes VRAM for 32k context\n - OLLAMA_NUM_GPU=-1 # Forces all layers to the 5070 Ti\n deploy:\n resources:\n reservations:\n devices:\n - driver: nvidia\n count: all\n capabilities: [gpu]\n\n # 2. THE LIBRARIAN (OpenClaw Orchestrator with GPT-5.4 Cloud-Link)\n apollo-agent:\n image: ghcr.io/openclaw/openclaw:latest\n container_name: apollo-agent\n ports:\n - \"18789:18789\"\n environment:\n - OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://ollama:11434\n - OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789\n - ALLOW_FILE_MODIFICATION=true\n - ALLOW_DESKTOP_INTERACTION=true\n - WORKSPACE_DIR=/home/node/.openclaw/workspace\n - GATEWAY_TOKEN=${APOLLO_TOKEN} # Authenticates via your .env file\n volumes:\n - C:/Apollo/Intel:/home/node/.openclaw\n - C:/Apollo/Intel/workspace:/home/node/.openclaw/workspace\n # Map the Vault as a sub-folder of the Workspace\n - C:/Apollo/Vault:/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/vault\n depends_on:\n - ollama\n command: [\"node\", \"dist/index.js\", \"gateway\"]\n restart: unless-stopped\n\n # 3. THE PURIFIER (HTML/PDF -> Markdown)\n docling:\n image: ghcr.io/docling-project/docling-serve:latest\n container_name: docling\n ports:\n - \"5001:5001\"\n volumes:\n - C:/Apollo/Vault/Raw:/root/apollo_raw # Ingestion Source\n - C:/Apollo/Vault/Clean:/root/apollo_clean # Purification Output\n\n # 4. THE MEMORY (LightRAG Knowledge Engine)\n lightrag:\n image: ghcr.io/hkuds/lightrag:latest\n container_name: apollo-lightrag\n ports:\n - \"9621:9621\"\n volumes:\n - C:/Apollo/Vault/Database:/app/data/rag_storage # Persistent Graph DB\n - C:/Apollo/Vault/Clean:/app/data/inputs # Only indexes Clean MD\n environment:\n - LLM_BINDING=ollama\n - LLM_BINDING_HOST=http://ollama:11434\n - LLM_MODEL=Apollo-Architect # Ministral 14B Q6_K\n - EMBEDDING_BINDING=ollama\n - EMBEDDING_BINDING_HOST=http://ollama:11434\n - EMBEDDING_MODEL=nomic-embed-text # Local vectorization\n - SUMMARY_CONTEXT_SIZE=32000 # 32k Context Priority\n depends_on:\n - ollama\n\n # 5. THE SCOUTS (Web Scraping & Stealth Browsing)\n browserless:\n image: browserless/chrome:latest\n container_name: browserless\n ports:\n - \"3003:3000\"\n restart: unless-stopped\n\n crawl4ai:\n image: unclecode/crawl4ai:latest\n container_name: apollo-scout\n ports:\n - \"11235:11235\"\n environment:\n - MAX_CONCURRENT_TASKS=3\n restart: unless-stopped\n\n # 6. THE CONDUCTORS (Automation & State Tracking)\n n8n:\n image: n8nio/n8n:latest\n container_name: n8n\n ports:\n - \"5678:5678\"\n environment:\n - N8N_HOST=0.0.0.0\n - N8N_PORT=5678\n - N8N_RUNNERS_ENABLED=true\n volumes:\n - ./data/n8n:/home/node/.n8n\n - C:/Apollo/Intel:/home/node/apollo_intel\n depends_on:\n - n8n_db\n\n n8n_db:\n image: postgres:16\n container_name: n8n_db\n environment:\n POSTGRES_USER: apollo_admin\n POSTGRES_PASSWORD: secure_password_2026\n POSTGRES_DB: apollo_state\n volumes:\n - ./data/postgres:/var/lib/postgresql/data\n\n # 7. THE INTERFACE (Human Dashboard)\n open-webui:\n image: ghcr.io/open-webui/open-webui:cuda\n container_name: open-webui\n ports:\n - \"3000:8080\"\n environment:\n - OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://ollama:11434\n - WEBUI_SECRET_KEY=apollo_v2_secret\n volumes:\n - ./data/open-webui:/app/backend/data\n - C:/Apollo/Intel:/app/backend/data/apollo_intel\n depends_on:\n - ollama"}],"timestamp":1776327808501}}
