ean/ingest/`\n- Retrieval-friendly summaries plus canonical evidence files\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/vault/Clean/projects/apollo/deliverables.md\",\"content\":\"# Apollo Deliverables\\n\\n## Completed\\n- Raw corpus inventory\\n- Exact duplicate report\\n- Probable duplicate report\\n- Initial and refined project classification\\n- Apollo timeline draft\\n- Aurelius timeline draft\\n- Project folder scaffolds\\n\\n## In progress\\n- Operational project docs suitable for retrieval and orchestration\\n- LightRAG-ready ingestion layout\\n\\n## Target deliverables\\n- Clean Apollo project memory pack\\n- Clean Aurelius project memory pack\\n- Shared-source handling for Gemini export material\\n- Stable ingestion structure under `vault/Clean/ingest/`\\n- Retrieval-friendly summaries plus canonical evidence files\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":163,"output":666,"cacheRead":39168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39997,"cost":{"input":0.00040750000000000004,"output":0.00999,"cacheRead":0.009792,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0201895}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776327967377,"responseId":"resp_0156872873475ee30169e09d1f5d7c819194334e8a4ecf1db2"}}
