{"type":"message","id":"b48bc336","parentId":"76d1a0b6","timestamp":"2026-04-16T13:29:24.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Yes. Tell me what you want the branch to focus on, and I’ll spin it up.\n\nBest candidates right now:\n1. Apollo corpus analysis\n2. Aurelius corpus analysis\n3. LightRAG ingestion workflow\n4. contradiction and gap analysis across both projects\n\nIf you want, I recommend **4** as the most valuable fork.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0156872873475ee30169e0e4339df88191919a527289163b8f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":150,"output":80,"cacheRead":60928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61158,"cost":{"input":0.000375,"output":0.0012000000000000001,"cacheRead":0.015231999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.016807}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776346161193,"responseId":"resp_0156872873475ee30169e0e431db54819194910147fc701934"}}
